Solubilization, renaturation and purification were performed in a manner similar to that described in Example 12. The following sequences were used:
Sequence of iFAP-PE24-LR-LO10R-456A-long-linker and LCL4-PE24-LR-LO10R-456A-long-linker chimeric full length heavy chain comprising the variable domain VH of SEQ ID NO: 93, a linker comprising the amino acid sequence of SEQ ID NO: 36, and a PE comprising SEQ ID NO: 37 (SEQ ID NO: 291);
Sequence LCL4-T20 chimeric heavy chain construct comprising the full length heavy chain comprising the variable domain VH of SEQ ID NO: 93, a linker comprising the amino acid sequence of SEQ ID NO: 36 and a PE comprising SEQ ID NO: 289 (T18/T20) (SEQ ID NO: 292);
Sequence of full length iFAP light chain (SEQ ID NO: 293) comprising the variable light chain domain of SEQ ID NO: 94 and constant region;
Sequence of full length LCL4 light chain (SEQ ID NO: 294) comprising the variable light chain domain of SEQ ID NO: 290 and constant region; and
Sequence of the variable light chain domain of SEQ ID NO: 290 (with mutation M4L at position 4 (compared to SEQ ID NO: 94).
